title: error
body:
every time i get into a champ select i get this error message saying "failed to proccess the message" and then some trash behind it

please help me

replies.body:
Hey there,

This is currently a [known issue](http://boards.oce.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/help-support-oce/BE08RpjY-my-client-keeps-getting-error-messages?comment=0001) and is being investigated.

I do not have any further updates or an ETA on a fix at this time.
